{"lemma":"عِزَّة","slug":"عِزَّة","root":"ع.ز.ز","root_slug":"ع-ز-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ز-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عِزَّة","root":"عزز","pos":"N","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28918","n28919","n29018","n29028"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"honour; power"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"group of people"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of the verb عَزَّ (ʕazza)."},"ipa":["/ʕiz.za/","/ʕi.za/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28918","headword_ar":"عَزَّةٌ","root":"Ez","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female young one of a gazelle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28919","headword_ar":"عِزَّةٌ","root":"Ez","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiz~N","text_ar":"عِزٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n29018","headword_ar":"عِزَةٌ","root":"Ezw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A party of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSobapN","text_ar":"عُصْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., as expl. in the O in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ESb","text_ar":"عصب"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who league together to defend one another"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceeding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as compose"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqap","text_ar":"حَلْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or, accord. to Er-Rághib,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a company of men who assert their relationship, one to another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by birth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the leaguing together for mutual aid:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [for] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for the final radical letter which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or, as some say, it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EazaY","text_ar":"عَزَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ he was, or became, patient; ” as though they were a company who took patience by one another's example: (TA:) [for, accord. to J,] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eizuwna","text_ar":"عِزُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euzuwna","text_ar":"عُزُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EizFY","text_ar":"عِزًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", but they did not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EizaAtN","text_ar":"عِزَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiziyna","text_ar":"عِزِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the Kur lxx. 37, (S, TA,) [expl. as] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"companies in a state of dispersion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sundry, parties:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EizapN","text_ar":"عِزَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is [said to be] originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EizowapN","text_ar":"عِزْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from [the inf. n.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEazowu","text_ar":"العَزْوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": as though each party asserted their relationship [as sons] to other than those to whom the other party asserted their relationship: (Ksh, Bd:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eizuwna","text_ar":"عِزُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. by Et-Tarasoosee as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"companies coming in a state of dispersion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Ald~aAri Eizuwna","text_ar":"فِى الدَّارِ عِزُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, are"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"several sorts of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","Ksh","Bd"]},{"entry_id":"n29028","headword_ar":"عِزَةٌ","root":"EzY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", held by some to belong to this art.: see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ezw","text_ar":"عزو"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}